  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旌旗恁飘荡，万骑皆龙骧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "渺渺戈纹贯落星，长幡早已动高旌。丈夫鹊印摇边月，大将龙韬旧有声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅，周遇吉。奉命镇守岱州等处。可恨闯贼统领大兵，直压城下，昨日与他"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爱子李洪基，连战数阵，看他有惧怯之意。怎奈他马骤如飞，不能擒获。今日"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "交锋，随机擒他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，杀上前去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（金钱花） 旌旗云绕，迷漫迷漫，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摆开阵势，城南城南。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擒虎兕寸心丹，擒虎兕寸心丹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.0,
        0.1667,
        0.6667,
        0.1667,
        0.0,
        1,
        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉",
        "李洪基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将遇良才，棋逢对手，越令人豪气频添，把精神抖擞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，李洪基。奉父命，提兵攻打岱州。那周遇吉，他将人马尽屯于城外，排成"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "犄角之势，使我兵不能前进，攻东则应东，攻西则应西，此乃以逸待劳，以寡"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敌众之计。前日与他交战数次，他的枪法神出鬼入，不能招架。只得诈败，诱"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他到来，俺使飞刀斩他，反被接住，掷来斩俺。亏俺的坐骑，乃千里驹，名曰"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪电光，若迟一步，险些被伤了。自从父王与我改名洪基，名字应了年号，只"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是叔父一支虎，有些妬忌。俺若招降此人，与俺作个心腹，传位天下，稳如磐"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "石。今日再去交锋，降伏此人便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众孩儿兵，杀上前去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（滴溜子） 催铁骑，催铁骑，如云骤，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挽金戈，挽金戈，如霜，光溜溜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各显威，神惊鬼愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、四上手、四小军同迎上，见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，周将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我生得恁般英雄，也算天下间一个好汉。可惜你生于末世，未逢明主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗，胡说！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺堂堂帝统御中州，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "版图四海全收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主弱臣庸，将见败亡耳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺圣上呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比隆尧舜功德茂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少甚么稷契皋夔名胄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅你一旅之师，济得甚事，为人也要见机而行，才是英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠和孝，平生自守，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身和命笑浮沤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，你昂昂气宇恁风流，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更艺勇可称琼玖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若倾心归顺，与你结为兄弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真果是，云龙风虎金兰友，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保毕世恩荣化胄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，周将军，你执意如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀头丧身家尽休，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄骨弃荒丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉 （急三枪） 俺心如铁，意如石，胆如天，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任你随何口，难动我寸心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基 （急三枪） 莫待钟鸣漏尽，山水穷头，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "灾星至，欲悔无由。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、李洪基同杀下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
