    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉",
        "李洪基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他枪法，十分厉害，不能取胜，待他来时，与他对刀，必然胜他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，周将军，我想凡为大将，十八般武艺，件件皆能，方为大将，你敢与俺对"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀乃兵家所用，怎么不知！就与你对。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（急三枪） 披风泼雪猛如彪，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、李洪基同杀下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李洪基→周遇吉",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "周遇吉→李洪基",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
