          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、四上手、四小军同迎上，见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，周将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我生得恁般英雄，也算天下间一个好汉。可惜你生于末世，未逢明主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗，胡说！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺堂堂帝统御中州，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "版图四海全收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主弱臣庸，将见败亡耳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺圣上呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比隆尧舜功德茂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少甚么稷契皋夔名胄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅你一旅之师，济得甚事，为人也要见机而行，才是英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠和孝，平生自守，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身和命笑浮沤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，你昂昂气宇恁风流，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更艺勇可称琼玖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若倾心归顺，与你结为兄弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真果是，云龙风虎金兰友，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保毕世恩荣化胄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，周将军，你执意如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀头丧身家尽休，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄骨弃荒丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉 （急三枪） 俺心如铁，意如石，胆如天，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任你随何口，难动我寸心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基 （急三枪） 莫待钟鸣漏尽，山水穷头，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "灾星至，欲悔无由。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、李洪基同杀下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他枪法，十分厉害，不能取胜，待他来时，与他对刀，必然胜他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，周将军，我想凡为大将，十八般武艺，件件皆能，方为大将，你敢与俺对"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀乃兵家所用，怎么不知！就与你对。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（急三枪） 披风泼雪猛如彪，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万丈寒光飞骤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边风声频吼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干羽振舞阶溜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、李洪基同杀下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的刀法，数年以来，并无对手，待他来时，与他比拳步战，必然成功。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这般畏怯潜逃，不像个英雄好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我马上武艺，彼此皆知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要怎样战法？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当初张飞与马超步战，杨再兴与庚丙文步战。俺如今与你比拳步战，若胜你不"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得，情愿收兵回去，永不犯你的边界。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和你较拳纵飞演，比进步，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这秘法可周知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且往。我为他马骤如飞，不能擒他，反与俺步战，岂非天赐我成功！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，李洪基！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待要撼天山穿云斗海蛟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺对你这小猕猴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将军，今日英雄遇英雄，好汉遇好汉，只可阵上赌输赢，不可暗箭伤人，方"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺平生，正直待人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，不可暗使冷箭者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狻猊摆尾下山头，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彩凤穿花唧溜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双展翅，鹰拿燕雀，龙探爪戏蛛球。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉喘。四上手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将他的营盘闪电光抢过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启元帅：闪电光抢过来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，记功领赏。摆队进关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜元帅，天神威武，擒此巨寇，威震华夷，小将等不胜忻贺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小丑虽擒，大逆尚存，何喜何贺？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看此子虽然年幼，英勇非常，何不亲解其缚，劝他降顺，岂不是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，你们哪里晓得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 他狼心野性岂驯柔，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暂降伏终成仇寇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 若留在关内呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 反贼内外难防守，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，加恩放回去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉 （煞尾） 纵猛虎归山差谬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅如何处治？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官听令：那闯贼知我擒他爱子，必然统领大兵，前来劫夺。这场厮杀非比"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小可，我军当预先准备，吩咐阵前，多排鹿角，广布蒺藜，头层藤牌手，二层"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "火炮手，三层弩弓手，第四层长枪手，第五层攒箭手，必须人人奋勇，个个当"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先，国家兴亡，在此一阵成功，奏凯论功升赏。众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 当一纶香饵在钩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要把鳌鱼钓，方得海波休！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
